OL,7,                                        
OL,8,  Teletext has been in the heart of     
OL,9,  Stroud for decades. In the 1970s MRG  
OL,10,  Systems started by manufacturing a    
OL,11,  Wireless World design for a decoder.  
OL,12,                                        
OL,13,  As well as supplying broadcasters     
OL,14,  across the globe it also made systems 
OL,15,  for displaying information to banks,  
OL,16,  cinemas and even air traffic control. 
OL,17,  All of this was delivered in teletext.
OL,18,                                        
OL,19,  All of this came to an end with the   
OL,20,  shutdown of analogue TV transmission. 
